  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Over 3000 children daily are being helped out of poverty through the schools, homes &amp; care that Hands Around the World&apos;s partner projects in Kenya, Zambia, Benin, Rwanda &amp; India provide. We are in the process of creating an emergency strategy to combat the urgent issues facing our projects as a result of Covid-19. This will allow HATW to continue to make a long-lasting difference in the young lives of those we support, whilst maximising the impact of available funding and minimising overheads.</narrative>
